Configuration:
  Simply add the function to your shell configuration file (~/.bashrc for bash, ~/.zshrc for zsh etc.)
  Important - you cannot set this as alias
  
Usage:
  def [term you want to define] [max amount of sentences]

Example usage:
  def oscilloscope 1

Example output:
  "An oscilloscope (informally scope or O-scope) is a type of electronic test instrument that graphically displays varying electrical voltages as a two-dimensional plot of one or more signals as a function of time."
